com.poesys.accounting.db.transaction.sql

Class AbstractQueryReimbursedItemsByItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.poesys.accounting.db.transaction.sql.AbstractQueryReimbursedItemsByItem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.poesys.db.dao.query.IParameterizedQuerySql<IItem,IItem>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    QueryReimbursedItemsByItem

    public abstract class AbstractQueryReimbursedItemsByItem
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.poesys.db.dao.query.IParameterizedQuerySql<IItem,IItem>

    A query Command pattern object that implements a SQL query of a collection of Item objects using the primary key of an associated Item object through the association ReimbursedItems using the association class Reimbursement. This association is a many-to-many association from Item to Item.

    This SQL specification contains a SQL statement that queries a collection of Item objects from the database table Item by joining to the database table Reimbursement and using the primary key from Item to query the collection.

    Author:
    Poesys/DB Cartridge
